    {
      "id": "knowledge-research-membership-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "V1 Proposal",
      "position": {
        "x": 1080,
        "y": -90
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## V1 Proposal\n\nApprove in v1:\n- `concept`\n- `claim`\n- `evidence`\n- `source`\n- `question`\n- `summary`\n\nDefer for later:\n- `definition`\n- `example`\n- `counterpoint`\n- `citation-note`\n\nRationale:\n- v1 should make evidence-backed reasoning possible without overfitting to academic citation machinery\n- deferred types can begin as fields, annotations, or typed relationships before they become dedicated node classes",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "views": [
            {
              "key": "markdown",
              "intent": "editor",
