    {
      "id": "knowledge-research-dependency-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Implementation Pressures",
      "position": {
        "x": 1080,
        "y": 320
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 420,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Implementation Pressures\n\nMinimum contracts:\n- `concept`: canonical label, aliases, optional description\n- `claim`: statement, stance or confidence, referenced evidence\n- `evidence`: excerpt, observation, or datum plus source locator\n- `source`: title, creator, kind, and durable identifier or URL\n- `question`: inquiry prompt, scope, and investigation status\n- `summary`: synthesized text plus explicit backing references\n\nLikely typed relationships:\n- `claim` supported-by or challenged-by `evidence`\n- `evidence` cites `source`\n- `question` investigates `concept` or `claim`\n- `summary` synthesizes a set of `claim` and `evidence` nodes\n\nMinimum runtime support:\n- durable provenance links with source locators\n- source attachment and citation metadata capture\n- claim/evidence summary rollups\n- filtered inquiry views and import/export for reference-heavy graphs",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "views": [
            {
              "key": "markdown",
              "intent": "editor",
              "payload": "editor.web",
              "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
              "source": "local",
              "version": ">=0.1.0"
            },
            {
